<h3><strong>Why This Matters</strong></h3>
<p>We‚Äôre entering a post-labor, post-institutional world. The academy is collapsing under the weight of its own rigidity.<br>
Emergent thinkers, self-teachers, and childlike philosophers need a home.<br>
<strong>MRU is that home.</strong><br>
